Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------PREV-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向联邦军全体将士通话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将开始进攻敌人要塞拉·格拉密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-FX的新模式调试已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫FX 爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央的敌人舰队是假像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令全军散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞炮为补充能量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下次发射前有一定间隔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央突破！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…不是什么误射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨那伦多的部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二波攻击队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着这一刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要为他们报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄恩·亚农
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔斯拜因 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿 高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里来的怪物 怎么还有这种机体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静 它看似威力强大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但武器好像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅限于前端的螺旋状光束炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转向能力也差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要冷静应对 不会是个可怕的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢帮忙 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型机？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带你去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你去看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向往的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定！
