Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人舰艇 迅速到位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要塞方向 正在形成一道防线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人舰队侧翼突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先支援歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用来提醒我战况严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如不形成突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为打破眼下的局势 只有这一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光子爆破炮在敌人阵型上打开大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那里突击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其后 成功突破的舰艇集中火力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接攻击敌人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 传令下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 光子爆破炮准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射后 向敌人宇宙要塞发起突击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿比斯队全体听令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先保护歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么 萨那伦多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢向我开火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是您误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是您在错误的时间出现在错误的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其实也非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是您的在场 可以击落更多敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听见我的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央区域不得部署舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没把你看作是伊泽尔坎特大人的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪格玛泽隆炮已经不能发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将根据战况独自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来 萨那伦多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨那伦多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和我作对到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手的行动太不规则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止这种战斗方式 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到刚才的惨状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下意识挡住了 值得夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但能招架到何时呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉德和戴蒙要你去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号在被敌人机动战士攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道怎么对付那东西 你快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨你 为什么来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像是当斗牛士的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别想继续横冲直撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教你的不是杀人手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在战场上求生的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是伊泽尔坎特大人的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长得简直和他像极了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球一定比这里更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望维甘和地球人都活得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 该死 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台机体的攻击方式太单一了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要了解它的攻击方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力再大也不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我怎么能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败在高达以外的机体手里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出这招以后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是个活动靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于让我逮住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你知道大言不惭的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接碾成肉罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经将死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先供应维生系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰内多处显示受损
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过主要动力系统还在运转
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮进入最终发射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射准备即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 命令射线轴上友军退避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 探测系统有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人舰艇上发现友军识别信号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是舍利奇队长的机体
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号在磨蹭什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是 射线轴上的敌舰附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我军机体被困
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法自行脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇队长 舍利奇队长 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮已经完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽快离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通讯系统运转正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇少校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌…歌姬号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮发射在即
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你立刻离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 完全动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…从驾驶舱逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外壳好像已经被撞得变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法… 一个人打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳图尔舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一击的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 快让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…机会转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人开始规避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令附近部队前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚发出撤离命令 周围无人可派
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左舷8区显示受损
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害控制三班 前往受损区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 歌姬号也难保
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时候 联邦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇少校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢…你所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇·阿比斯 结束通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贵舰好运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经是位合格的舰长了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会是个漫长的假期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇机信号消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破敌人防线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 敌人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄恩 是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么你会在机动战士里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向露乌保证过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会带她去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算对手是你 我也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 狄恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大家互相体谅 不用战争也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是猴年马月的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年后？一百年后？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说只有趁自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着的时候 赌眼前这场战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想看到再有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看到大家都好好地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想让狄恩活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…想在地球上风景最美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为露乌立一座墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周 开满她最爱的花儿 漫山遍野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放眼望去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜子般的湖面 延伸到天边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时常来看露乌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 狄恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还是要我亲自出马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就送你归西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把狄恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去战斗力的机动战士就是一堆废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是在清理垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的手里 让它废物利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一堆垃圾 也该心满意足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不饶你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不饶你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部队 报告损失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨那伦多部队 伤亡惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要塞防线有崩溃迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人舰队开始发起突击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投入所有预备队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他们轻而易举突破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今我还在犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同敌人舰队一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排除所有妨碍计划的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须抵达伊甸
